div.p: Compertimenta pictoriis flosculis manubiis que bellicis variegata. Auctore lacobo floro Antuer Hieron Cock exud Antuerpie 1567.
Cartouches decorated with little flowers and the spoils of war. Authored by Jacob Floris, in Antwerp. Published by Hieronymus Cock, in Antwerp, 1567.
